<i>THE HIGHER YOUR CLOUD,</i>
<i>THE FURTHER YOUR RAIN FALLS.</i>

1316
01:05:32,062 --> 01:05:34,462
IT'S FULL OF LITERARY STUFF.

1317
01:05:34,464 --> 01:05:36,932
THREE DOLLARS.

1318
01:05:36,934 --> 01:05:39,467
<i>I SOON LEARNED</i>
<i>THAT WHEN IT RAINS</i>

1319
01:05:39,469 --> 01:05:41,036
<i>IT POURS.</i>

1320
01:05:41,038 --> 01:05:42,404
ALL RIGHT.

1321
01:05:42,406 --> 01:05:44,539
I'M SORRY.
CAN YOU REPEAT THAT?

1322
