THEY WON'T LET YOU REAPPLY.

1323
01:05:46,576 --> 01:05:49,577
YOU WERE ACCEPTED,
BUT YOU NEVER CONFIRMED.

1324
01:05:49,579 --> 01:05:51,413
SO YOU WERE DENIED.

1325
01:05:51,415 --> 01:05:54,950
NO, IT MUST'VE GOTTEN LOST
IN THE MAIL. I...

1326
01:05:54,952 --> 01:05:57,252
