YOU DON'T WANT TO REMEMBER...

1405
01:11:58,615 --> 01:12:00,515
EVERYTHING.

1406
01:12:00,517 --> 01:12:03,318
WHAT ISN'T WORTH REMEMBERING?

1407
01:12:03,320 --> 01:12:07,021
WITH GOOD MEMORIES
