1408
01:12:07,023 --> 01:12:09,357
AND I'VE GOT A LOT OF BOTH.

1409
01:12:09,359 --> 01:12:12,760
AT LEAST THIS WAY
I CAN FAST FORWARD THROUGH
ALL THE BAD STUFF.

1410
01:12:12,762 --> 01:12:14,629
A COUNSELOR ONCE TOLD ME

1411
01:12:14,631 --> 01:12:17,065
